      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Password Criteria</title>
         <div class="- topic/div ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">All new passwords must meet the following criteria:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Each access level must have a unique password.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The password must consist of 8 to 16 characters.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">The password must consist of at least 1 of the special characters,
see the table below.</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </div>
         <p class="- topic/p ">When entering a password, the numbers 0–9
are entered using the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Number keys</b>. Letters and special characters
are entered by cycling through the list of available password letters
and characters with the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow up key</b> and the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Arrow down
key</b>.</p>
         <note class="- topic/note ">To delete the last entered character press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">C key</b>.</note>
