      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Login to Master Mode and How to a Change Password</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To access the change password feature a login to the master mode
is needed.<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press both the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clock/number 1 key</b> and the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Number
2 key</b> at the same time. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Master
Password: </codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the numpad keys to enter the password for <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Master Mode</b>. Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to confirm. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Enter Password:</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the numpad keys to enter the password for <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Change Password</b>. Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to confirm.  The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will
show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Change Password:</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the numpad keys to enter the existing password for the
access level you want to change, for example if changing the default
master mode password enter <codeph translate="no" class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">111111</codeph>.
Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to confirm. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Enter New PW:</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the numpad numbers and arrow keys to enter a new password
consisting of at least 8 characters, including at least 1 special
character. Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to confirm. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Confirm New PW:</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the numpad keys to repeat the new password. Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b> to confirm.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>The password is changed.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Logout from Master Mode</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To logout from master
mode manually:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press both the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Clock/number 1 key</b> and the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Number
2 key</b> at the same time. The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Display</b> will show <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Enter
Password:</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Number 6 key</b> and then confirm with the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Hash key</b>.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>You are now logged out from master mode.</p>
         <note class="- topic/note ">If no numpad
key is pressed for 2 minutes you are automatically logged out from
master mode.</note>
